            <div class="ph__label">Hero — Product Shot</div>
            <div class="ph__sub">The Orivo purifier pen, three botanicals, packaging.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="gal-slide">
          <div class="ph">
            <svg width="92" height="92" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3a4 4 0 0 0-4 4c0 1.5-1 2.5-2 3.5"/><path d="M12 3a4 4 0 0 1 4 4c0 1.5 1 2.5 2 3.5"/><path d="M6 10.5C6 15 9 18 12 21c3-3 6-6 6-10.5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1"/></svg>
            <div class="ph__label">The Swap</div>
            <div class="ph__sub">Reach for this instead of a cigarette · no nicotine · cool hit.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="gal-slide">
          <div class="ph">
            <svg width="92" height="92" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg>
            <div class="ph__label">How To Use</div>
            <div class="ph__sub">When the craving hits: inhale · hold · exhale. No setup.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
