<!-- ============================================================
     6 · OBJECTION-HANDLING FAQ
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="section" id="faq">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head" style="margin-bottom:36px;">
      <div class="eyebrow">Still on the fence?</div>
      <h2>Honest answers to the real reasons people hesitate</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="acc">
      <div class="acc__item">
        <button class="acc__q">"I've tried everything to quit — why would this be different?" <span class="ico"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></span></button>
        <div class="acc__a"><div>Because everything you tried went after the <b>nicotine</b> — or relied on raw willpower — and left the <b>habit</b> untouched. Patches and gum dose you with the chemical but give your hands and mouth nothing to do. Orivo is the opposite: it hands the ritual back to you — the reach, the breath, the cool hit — without any tobacco or nicotine. You're replacing the <em>act</em>, which is the part that usually drags people back.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="acc__item">
        <button class="acc__q">"Is this just vaping? Is there nicotine in it?" <span class="ico"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></span></button>
        <div class="acc__a"><div>No. There is <b>no nicotine, no tobacco, no combustion and nothing synthetic</b> — nothing is burned. It's a cool botanical vapour from just three ingredients: Mullein leaf, Thyme and Mint. You're not swapping one addiction for another, because there's nothing addictive in it to get hooked on.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="acc__item">
        <button class="acc__q">"Shouldn't I be able to quit on willpower alone?" <span class="ico"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></span></button>
        <div class="acc__a"><div>Relapsing isn't weakness — it's an <b>unanswered habit.</b> The hand-to-mouth ritual is wired into a hundred moments of your day, and willpower alone has to fight every one of them. Using a tool to take that fight off your plate isn't cheating; it's just giving yourself something to reach for so the old reflex has somewhere else to go.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="acc__item">
        <button class="acc__q">"Will it actually stop the cravings, or is it placebo?" <span class="ico"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></span></button>
        <div class="acc__a"><div>The cool hit and the hand-to-mouth action answer the urge <b>in the moment</b> — that part most people feel on the very first breath. Whether it helps you cut down over the following weeks is what our customers report, and we're honest that it varies from person to person. That's exactly why every order is backed by a 30-day money-back guarantee — so you can find out risk-free.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="acc__item">
        <button class="acc__q">"I've smoked for decades — is it too late for me?" <span class="ico"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></span></button>
        <div class="acc__a"><div>Plenty of our customers are 40- and 50-year smokers, and most are over 50. There's no judgement and no lectures here. One note for honesty: Orivo is a botanical <b>aromatherapy product for adult use — not a medicine, a medical device or a nicotine-replacement therapy.</b> If you have a heart or lung condition, are pregnant, or take medication, please check with your doctor first.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="acc__item">
        <button class="acc__q">"What if it doesn't help me quit?" <span class="ico"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></span></button>
        <div class="acc__a"><div>Then you send it back. You have a full <b>30 days to try it — even with the box open</b> — for a complete refund, plus 90 days for easy returns. Put it through your hardest triggers: the morning coffee, the drive, the after-dinner urge. If it isn't helping you reach for fewer cigarettes, it costs you nothing. The risk is entirely ours.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="acc__item">
        <button class="acc__q">"How long does a pen last — and is it cheaper than smoking?" <span class="ico"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></span></button>
        <div class="acc__a"><div>Each pen is about a <b>30-day supply</b>, with nothing to charge or refill. And the maths is hard to argue with: a pack-a-day habit adds up to <b>well over R1,000 every month</b> — the best-value bundle is R1,999 for roughly five months. Most people choose a multi-pack so they never run out mid-quit.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="acc__item">
        <button class="acc__q">"Is this a subscription? Any hidden charges?" <span class="ico"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></span></button>
        <div class="acc__a"><div>No. It's a <b>one-time purchase at one clear price</b> — no subscription, no auto-billing, no surprises on your statement. You order once, it ships within 24 hours, and you only come back for more if it's working for you.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

